**HARDWARE TERMS**
  # There are mainly two types of computer hardware: Internal and external hardware components.

Internal hardware components are devices built into the motherboard or added as an expansion card or device to the computer.
The most important internal hardware components are RAM, Hard disk, SSD, Monitor, and CPU. 
The motherboard connects all the other components, and it is the backbone of the computer system.
        1. Motherboard
